---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | J&C Asphalt"
  description="Privacy policy for J&C Asphalt. Learn how we collect, use, and protect the information you submit through our website."
>
  <section class="policy-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="section-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p>Last updated: June 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="policy-body">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="policy-content">

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2>Overview</h2>
          <p>J&C Asphalt ("we," "our," or "us") operates the website jcasphaltpaving.com. This page explains what information we collect when you use our website, how we use it, and how we protect it.</p>
          <p>We do not sell, trade, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>We collect information you voluntarily provide when you fill out our quote request form. This may include:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>First and last name</li>
            <li>Phone number</li>
            <li>Email address</li>
            <li>Project address</li>
            <li>Service type and project details</li>
          </ul>
          <p>We do not collect payment information through this website.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>The information you submit through our contact form is used solely to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Respond to your quote request</li>
            <li>Contact you to schedule an estimate or discuss your project</li>
            <li>Send information relevant to your inquiry</li>
          </ul>
          <p>We will not add you to a mailing list or contact you for unrelated purposes without your consent.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p>Our contact form is processed through <strong>Web3Forms</strong> (web3forms.com), a third-party form submission service. When you submit a quote request, your information is transmitted to Web3Forms and then forwarded to our email inbox. Web3Forms has its own privacy policy governing how they handle data in transit.</p>
          <p>Our website is hosted on <strong>Vercel</strong> (vercel.com). Vercel may collect standard server logs including IP addresses and browser information as part of normal hosting operations.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2>Cookies</h2>
          <p>This website does not use tracking cookies or advertising cookies. Standard browser and hosting logs may be retained for security and performance purposes.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2>Data Retention</h2>
          <p>Quote request information is retained in our email inbox for as long as needed to respond to your inquiry and manage our business records. You may request deletion of your information at any time by contacting us directly.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2>Text Messaging (SMS)</h2>
          <p>Text us at (801) 941-4398 for a free paving estimate. By texting, you agree to receive SMS from JC Asphalt. Msg frequency varies (up to ~6 msgs/mo). Msg &amp; data rates may apply. Reply STOP to opt out, HELP for help. See our Privacy Policy.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2>Your Rights</h2>
          <p>You have the right to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Request a copy of the information we have about you</li>
            <li>Request that we correct or delete your information</li>
            <li>Opt out of any future communication from us</li>
          </ul>
          <p>To exercise any of these rights, contact us using the information below.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2>Contact</h2>
          <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy or how your information is handled, you can reach us at:</p>
          <ul class="contact-list">
            <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:jcasphalt.contracting@gmail.com">jcasphalt.contracting@gmail.com</a></li>
            <li><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:+18019414398">(801) 941-4398</a></li>
            <li><strong>Location:</strong> Orem, Utah</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated date at the top.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .policy-hero {
    padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
    background-color: #FFFFFF;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #cd553f;
  }

  .policy-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .policy-hero p {
    color: #888;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .policy-body {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background-color: #F2F5F2;
  }

  .policy-content {
    max-width: 760px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .policy-section h2 {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: #121212;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #cd553f;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .policy-section p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .policy-section p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .policy-section ul {
    margin: 0.75rem 0 0.75rem 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .policy-section li {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .contact-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin-left: 0;
  }

  .contact-list a {
    color: #cd553f;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .contact-list a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
